    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Substances that conduct electric current resulting from positive and negative ions discharged at terminals (cathode and anode) of an electric circuit, specifically the conducting fluid used in a battery.</Note_Text>
